content: madjin: Focused on documentation improvements, merging PR #2828 which added new README files and reorganized existing ones (+2564/-122 lines). Created 6 issues related to documentation and feature improvements, all of which were closed, including #2825 for adding missing README files and #3083 for adding troubleshooting FAQs to the docs. Contributed significantly to the codebase with 35 commits modifying 118 files (+5415/-711 lines), with 94% of changes focused on feature work. Activity was sporadic, concentrated on just 3 days this month, with contributions split between code (57%) and documentation (33%).
